    show pov shocked at left
    show jac smirk_talk at right
    jac "I don’t feel it’s fair that I’m being asked to help out just because things went to shit, you know?"
    show pov angry at left
    show jac angry_talk at right
    jac "Especially because I would have been more than happy to continue helping out but it seems like I wasn't needed anymore and tossed aside."

