    show pov angry_talk at left
    show jac smirk at right
    pov "Even Effie told you to cool it down and I know you respect her opinion over everyone else so can’t you at least tell me what the heck is up with you to be so jerkish with me lately?!"
    show pov shocked at left
    show jac angry_talk at right
    jac "Don’t you think it should be obvious by now?!"
    show pov angry at left
    show jac shocked_talk at right
    jac "I haven’t exactly been subtle about it and I would have hoped you picked up the signals by now."
    show pov angry_talk at left
    show jac shocked at right
