    show jac bored at right
    pov "Maybe I do know what’s going on, but I still want to hear you up and say it!"
    show pov shocked_talk at left
    show jac confused at right
    pov "You are my best friend, man. We agreed we wouldn’t keep secrets from each other, didn’t we?!"

